import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import Head from 'next/head'
import Header from './Header'

export default (props) => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Head>
        <link
          rel="stylesheet"
          href="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.css"
        />
      </Head>

      <Header />
      {props.children}
    </Container>
  )
}
